	<p>Tynan is right on.<br />
<br />
Trueshot lowers your dps at the moment.<br />
<br />
I was jolting every 4 shots with Trueshot, and sadly after 3 rounds of this, I got a resist on jolt, and shot 4 more times, summoned, dead.<br />
<br />
On a 2 minute disc, having to stop and wait while you recast jolt is absurd.<br />
<br />
The silly thing is that I hit the trueshot disc after Pyronis was already under half health, and I never once had a hit over 1200 on a shot (embarassing really).<br />
<br />
I am assuming this situation is a bug they will fix.  If it is not, a mere refund of aa is not going to cut it.<br />
<br />
I am a bit upset with the current situation, but I have to assume that they made a mistake and intend to fix it, and have just dropped the ball on communicating what's going on (play a bard and you will be more used to this).</p>
	
	
	
