 What the Devs did they did knowing full well that using our Disc would get us summoned and killed further everything SoE did with the archery aa's were done with the sole purpose of increasing the amount of damage that could be done with archery.  Despite the fact that this is supposed to effect all classes equally our class as well as any class that spent aa's to increase the amount of damage done by ranged effects deserves a refund of their aa points.  You can't expect people to spend the time and effort to acquire aa points specifically to increase damage and then nerf them without regard.   SoE has once again broken the faith with it's customer base "fixing" a non issue that hurt no one and made the game fun for many without being over balancing.</p>
	
	
	
