	<p>I didn't have any problems with Archery aggro all day yesterday.<br />
Sure in BoT if I used archery without jolting and casted a nuke or two I would get summoned once or twice during the fight. Generally after the pull, I'd wait for 3-5 bow hits, then jolt once and I wouldn't get summoned the rest of the fight.<br />
<br />
Also, used TS on IV fight yesterday and I didn't get summoned at all. However his guards were summoning me like crazy while clearing.<br />
<br />
Primal Bow, am3/EQ, buffs and such.<br />
<br />
