100% increase to damage but now I will have to decrease the number of shots I take by nearly 50% due to waiting and pausing and jolting.<br />
Once you have to jolt as much as is required (I was triple jolting and still getting summoned /laugh) you will not possibly outdamage your melee dps.<br />
My archery AA sucks for soloing. It takes me (with trueshot and haste) 8-10 min to kill a Nophtan in PoS. It takes me + wizard about 3 min (or less) with me snaring and the wizard nuking. Where is the leet soloing you speak of?</p>
	
	
	
