	<td class="alt1" valign="top">
	
	<!-- message -->
	<p>I'm not really sure WHAT SoE is trying to accomplish with these changes.  Looking back, I'm pretty sure they knew that this was going to affect Wizards, Mages, Necros, Rangers and all ranged dps classes in a HUGE way.<br />
<br />
First, they gave the elemental nameds and gods aoe rampage and huge AE's...this effectively nerfed all melee's into non-importance on these fights.  THEN, they turn around and change the way the hate list works and now any wizard, necro, mage that does ANYTHING, even waiting until super late in the fight gets near instant aggro and rampage and dies.  This effectively makes casters useless agains these mobs.<br />
<br />
If they knew the kind of effect this change would have, then they need to SERIOUSLY look at the ability of Warriors to generate and keep/lock aggro...because as it is I think it is completely broken.  Dual EB wielding warriors who tank a mob for 3 minutes lose aggro instantly to a wizard who casts his FIRST nuke? C'mon thats ridiculous!<br />
<br />
Rampage is also super FUBAR'd, apparently they've decided to scrap the Luclin and PoP rampage and go back to a modified Velious rampage rule set where aoe rampage still exists in some form.  I just don't know how to describe it...it is that ****ed up.<br />
<br />
As for rangers and our aggro well....If you use archery AND nuke you WILL get summoned by any kind of mob, be it xp mob in Fire or a boss mob ( and that is while using jolt ).  If you are just using archery on boss mobs I found myself jolting every 4-5 shots and I was ok unless the MT died and then I was the first one or close to first ( other rangers ) to be summoned.<br />
<br />
I think Rangers are ok, aggro wise as long as you jolt like a mad man....but since I have had to start using jolt again I realize we REALLY REALLY NEED A LURE OR ICE BASED JOLT!<br />
<br />
Having to cast jolt every 4-5 bow shots just doesn't cut it when you are going to get resisted 66% of the time and so have to cast 2-3 more times before you can resume shooting. ( and this is NOT counting fizzles )<br />
<br />
GIVE US A LURE OR ICE BASED JOLT. AND FIX THE HATE LIST/RAMPAGE ISSUE.<blockquote><span class="smallfont">Quote:</span><hr size="1" />Originally Posted by <b>Ailbe</b><br /><i>Thats got me confused as well Tetrass...  I agree with you that it seems they did this at a very strange time, when people were actually happy with their classes.  /shrug...  Ok, well back to DAOC for me for the time being.</i><hr size="1" /></blockquote></p>
	
	
	
